org.apache.paimon.format.parquet.newreader

Interface VectorizedValuesReader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VectorizedDeltaBinaryPackedReader, VectorizedDeltaByteArrayReader, VectorizedDeltaLengthByteArrayReader, VectorizedPlainValuesReader, VectorizedReaderBase, VectorizedRleValuesReader

    public interface VectorizedValuesReader
    Interface for value decoding that supports vectorized (aka batched) decoding.
